 3D rendering. With a bonding capacity for large projects, low EMR, IIPP, and safety plans in place, Red Wave Communications is capable of handling all your residential and business design and integration needs with helpful and convenient customer service.'),(579,118,'wpcf-about-us-content-list',''),(580,118,'wpcf-certification-list','<b>Small Business</b>\r\nThis certification promotes California’s small business, and encourages sustained economic prosperity through working together to maintain the strength of small businesses throughout California.'),(581,118,'wpcf-certification-list','<b>NICET</b>\r\nThe National Institute for Certification in Engineering Technologies was created by the National Society of Professional Engineers to serve the certification needs of the engineering technology community.\r\n'),(582,118,'wpcf-certification-list','<b>BICSI</b>\r\n<i>The Building Industry Consulting Service International</i> is a credential and assurance that an individual has knowledge in a designated area of information technology, systems design, or installation.\r\n'),(583,118,'wpcf-certification-list','<b>RCDD</b>\r\nRegistered Communications Distribution Designer demonstrated their knowledge in the design, implementation and integration of information technology, and related infrastructure.\r\n'),(584,118,'wpcf-certification-list','<b>NFPA</b>\r\nNational Fire Protection Association provides codes, standards, research, training, and education for all of its members in public safety and fire safety.\r\n'),(585,118,'wpcf-certification-list','<b>BSIS</b>\r\nBureau of Security and Investigated Service registers certified, professional security guards in the state of California.\r\n'),(586,120,'_edit_last','1'),(587,120,'_edit_lock','1425332739:1'),(588,120,'wpcf-system-name','Systems'),(589,120,'wpcf-system-description','We are partnered with leading technology manufacturers to customize the right solution.'),(590,120,'wpcf-system-list',''),(591,120,'_wpcf-system-lis