tem','Project Coordination & Setup'),(1302,101,'wpcf-service-name','Build'),(1303,101,'wpcf-service-description','Red Wave Communications ensures the utmost professionalism when providing our services while incorporating the most efficient and latest technology, industry standard practices, project analysis, project management, and cost effective, timely results.'),(1304,101,'wpcf-service-list-item','Pre-construction Services'),(1305,101,'wpcf-service-list-item','Engineering & Job Analysis'),(1306,101,'wpcf-service-list-item','Budget & Estimating'),(1307,101,'wpcf-service-list-item','Scheduling'),(1308,101,'wpcf-service-list-item','Job site Coordination'),(1309,101,'wpcf-service-list-item','Finalizing Job Completion'),(1310,103,'wpcf-service-name','Maintain'),(1311,103,'wpcf-service-description','Red Wave Communications’ service department maintains, tests, and inspects a wide range of facilities in California. We support everything from small, family-owned restaurants to enterprise corporations like regional hospitals. We offer the most experienced and efficient technicians who are provided with the latest tools and technology to improve the identification and repair of nearly all types of communications, safety, and low voltage systems in secured and unsecured buildings.'),(1312,103,'wpcf-service-list-item','Two hour response time'),(1313,103,'wpcf-service-list-item','24/7 service 365 days a year'),(1314,103,'wpcf-service-list-item','Diagnosis and repair of fire panels, sound equipment, cameras, AV, data, access control systems, video surveillance, automation, and more.'),(1315,103,'wpcf-service-list-item','System Network Integration'),(1316,103,'wpcf-service-list-item','Inspection Compliance Reporting by BuildingReports'),(1317,103,'wpcf-service-list-item','Test & inspect'),(1318,103,'wpcf-service-list-item','Remote service capabilities'),(1319,103,'wpcf-service-list-item','Offsite data management'),(1344,71,'_wp_old_slug','audio-video'),(1363,80,'wpcf-system-name','Business Automation'),(1364,80,'wpcf-system-description','With automation, the possibilities are endless. Red Wave Communications partners with some of today’s leading manufacturers and designers to get the solution you need. We can design an all purpose control for your business that incorporates lighting, sound, music, networking, video, security, temperature control, cameras, gate control, and more.'),(1365,80,'wpcf-system-list','Control4'),(1366,80,'wpcf-system-list','Crestron'),(1367,80,'wpcf-system-list','Extron Electronics'),(1372,82,'wpcf-system-name','Master Clock and PA Systems'),(1373,82,'wpcf-system-description','Red Wave Communications has partnered with Sapling who features a complete line of digital clock products for systems such as Wired, IP, TalkBack, and the synchronized wireless clock system which is based upon their patented frequency-hopping technology that has transformed the industry. We meticulously design sound and communications technologies to perform flawlessly on their own, efficiently with one another, and communicate with third party systems.'),(1374,82,'wpcf-system-list','Sapling'),(1375,82,'wpcf-system-list','Telecor'),(1376,84,'wpcf-system-name','Nurse Call'),(1377,84,'wpcf-system-description','To meet the growing demands of the healthcare industry, we offer top of the line nurse call systems providing both effective communication solutions and simple to use equipment.'),(1378,84,'wpcf-system-list','Jeron'),(1406,151,'wpcf-link','residential/#accordionPro214-slide-3'),(1407,150,'wpcf-link','residential/#accordionPro214-slide-4'),(1427,152,'wpcf-link','/residential/#accordionPro214-slide-2'),(1429,158,'wpcf-link','business/#accordionPro213-slide-2'),(1430,157,'wpcf-link','business/#accordionPro213-slide-3'),(1431,156,'wpcf-link','business/#accordionPro213-slide-4'),(1432,154,'wpcf-link','business/#accordionPro213-slide-5'),(1433,132,'wpcf-link','business/#accordionPro213-slide-6'),(1434,155,'wpcf-link','business/#accordionPro213